cova.data.taints

Class SourceTaint

  • java.lang.Object
    • cova.data.taints.AbstractTaint
      • cova.data.taints.SymbolicTaint
        • cova.data.taints.SourceTaint

  • public class SourceTaint
extends SymbolicTaint
    The Class SourceTaint contains all information of a source taint.

    Source taints are created by SourceTaintCreationRule at statements that contain a source of type such as SourceField, SourceMethod or SourceUICallback.
